data.description: Presenting a prime investment opportunity, this move-in ready townhouse-style multi-family home features 4 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms, with an abundance of natural light illuminating the space. The modern farmhouse kitchen is equipped with stainless steel appliances, creating an inviting atmosphere for both residents and guests.  Adding to its appeal, the finished basement provides versatility and potential for a third income stream. Strategically located, the property is in close proximity to highways and within walking distance to NYC trains, making it a commuter's delight. Low taxes enhance the financial advantages of this investment.This residence is not only a functional living space but also an attractive prospect for those seeking a sound investment with great income potential. Take advantage of this opportunity to own a property that combines modern comfort, strategic location, and financial promise. Schedule a viewing today to explore the possibilities firsthand.
